Metropolition Ave., north side, west of Nurge Ave. the two homes from fore to background were known as 1439 A and 1439 Metropolitan Ave., in 1922. The Miller house adjoins the white house. In 1929 it was designated as number 2007 Metropolitan Ave.
1922
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.  MAY BE REPRODUCED.
